Simple Java program, which purpose is to send an email when a new file in scanned folder is discovered.

src - Java sources for this program
distro/config/file2.mail.properties - main configuration of program
distro/config/logging.properties - logging confguration
distro/config/mail-template.html - template used as an email

Maven2 is being used to create final zip distro, which is ready to run as is.

